        <section class="text">
            All manifest files should contain which of the following tags?
        </section>
        <section class="answer" data-correct > &ltapplication&gt</section>
        <section class="answer"> &ltpermission&gt </section>
        <section class="answer"> &ltuses-configuration&gt </section>
        <section class="answer"> &ltuses-feature&gt </section>
        <section class="answer"> &ltcompatible-screens&gt </section>
        <section class="description">
            All manifest files should contain &ltapplication&gt tag. Please take more time with <a href="https://developer.android.com/guide/topics/manifest/manifest-element.html/">third party links</a> provided through course videos. 
        </section>
